{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ko tee Rahpuri atlizzina/\nto ehd tee Siffeni/ un ko tee Sif-\nfeni atlizzina/ to ehd tahs Wab-\nboles/ un ko tahs Wabboles at-\nlizzina/ to ehd tee Kukkaini.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Uhsmohsteetees juhs Pee-\nDsehrutchee/ un raudajt/ un kau-\nzeet wiſſi Wihna-Plihtneeki\npahr to jaunu Wihnu/ jo tas irr\nno juhsas Muttes atrauts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo weena Tauta zellahs jeet juhs Preesterti/ kanzeet j\nprett mannu Semmi/ warrena Altara Sullaini/ eita/ palee\nun neskaitama/ winnas Sohbi Maisfös zaur Nakti/ juhs G\nir Lauwas Sobbi/ un winxai laixi manna Deewa/ jo Ehdar\nir Dserroftti ka weenain wez-\nzam Lauwani.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta irr mannu Wihna-\nKohku pohsta darrijsft/ un man-\nnu Wihges-Kohku par Put-\ntahm/ winna irr to miseht no-\nnisejti un apgahsuft/ winxa\nSarri irr balti tappufschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Waidi ka weena Jumpra-\nwa/ kas ar weenn Maisfu irr ap-\njobsutees tawa Bruhdgana\npehz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ehdamo-Uppuris/ un\nDseriamo-Uppuris irr no ta\nKUNGA Namma atrauts/ tee\nPreestert/ ta KUNGA Sullaini\nbehdajahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Tihruns irr poh-\nstihts/ ta Semme irr nostum-\nmusi/ jo ta Labbiba irr pohstitta/\ntas Wihns irr fakaltis/ un ta\nEtje eet bohja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee Arraji tohp Kauna/\nWihna-Dahrsneeki kauz par\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Wihna-Kohks\nfakaltis/ un tas Wihges-Ko\neet bohja/ tas Granatu-Ahbo\nKohks/ ir tas Palmu-Rehks\nAhbotu-Kohks/ wiſſi Kohki L\nka irr nokaltuschi/ un ta Lil\nmiba irr nonihkuſi pee teem\nweku Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Apjohsteetes/ un sche\nwent/ isfauzeet weenu Sap-\nnaschanas Deenu/ pulzin-\ntohs Wezzajus/ wiſſus S\nmes Eedsihwotajns uhs to N\nmu ta KUNGA juhsu Dee\nun peesanzeet to KUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Swehtijeet weenn\nwent/ isfauzeet weenu Sap-\nnaschanas Deenu/ pulzin-\ntohs Wezzajus/ wiſſus S\nmes Eedsihwotajns uhs to N\nmu ta KUNGA juhsu Dee\nun peesanzeet to KUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Waj pahr to Deenu\nta KUNGA Deena irr tu-\nun nahks ka weena Pohstisch\nno ta Wiſſuwarrena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi ta Barriba\npreekſch muhsahn Azzim at-\nta? Preeks un Libgsniiba n\nNamma muhsu Deewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Graudi irr app-\nPihtehn fatruhdeifschi/ tee M\ntu-Nammi irr pohstitti/\nSchuhzi irr faqruuschi/\nLabbiba irr nokaitusi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ak! ka waid tee Lo\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
